{
  "page": "Pepper Coast",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Pepper Coast</b> is a region noted for its corsairs. It's exact location is unknown.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pepper_Coast&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/83_AC\" title=\"83 AC\">83&#160;AC</a>, in preparation for his invasion of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlands</a>, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Morion_Martell\" title=\"Morion Martell\">Morion Martell</a> hired fleets from the pirates of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stepstones\" title=\"Stepstones\">Stepstones</a>, the sellsails of <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myr</a>, and the corsairs of the Pepper Coast to invade the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>. However, it took the better part of a year to gather all his strength, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">the Targaryens</a> had known about <a href=\"/index.php/Fourth_Dornish_War\" title=\"Fourth Dornish War\">the upcoming attack</a> for half a year in advance, in part due to the indiscretion of the pirates, sellsails, and corsairs. After the defeat of Morion's army in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_84_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">84&#160;AC</a>, the corsairs of the Pepper Coast became less troublesome for a while.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pepper_Coast&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Long Reign - Jaehaerys and Alysanne: Policy, Progeny, and Pain.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403210159\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.040 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 133/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8591/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 754/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 339/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 831/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   35.925      1 -total\n 80.79%   29.025      2 Template:Date\n 14.52%    5.215      1 Template:Ref\n  9.46%    3.398      1 Template:Ref/core\n  3.83%    1.375      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache wit